red Items\n43: \n44: The following items were deferred for future implementation:\n45: \n46: - Unit tests for all binaries\n47: - Integration tests\n48: - Static analysis (go vet, gofmt)\n49: - Makefile build targets\n50: - README documentation for each binary\n51: - Environment variable support testing\n52: - Project documentation updates\n\n(End of file - total 52 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-019 — CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-019\n- **Title**: CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n- **Module**: cmd\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Completed\n\n## Description\n\nImplemented 4 CLI binary entry points for managing AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter Kubernetes resources:\n\n1. **agentcube** - Main unified CLI with subcommands for managing both resource types\n2. **agent-runtime** - Dedicated CLI for AgentRuntime resource operations\n3. **code-interpreter** - Dedicated CLI for CodeInterpreter resource operations\n4. **agentcube-util** - Utility CLI for validation, diagnostics, and completion generation\n\n## Dependencies","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-019/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775876505482,"end":1775876505505}}}}
