ult: \"8080\")\n33: - [ ] Verify --workspace flag is defined (default: \"\")\n34: - [ ] Verify klog is initialized\n35: - [ ] Verify picod.NewServer is called with proper config\n36: - [ ] Verify signal handlers are configured (SIGINT, SIGTERM)\n37: - [ ] Verify graceful shutdown is implemented with 30s timeout\n38: \n39: **Verification**: Run `go build ./cmd/picod` and verify binary compiles successfully\n40: \n41: ---\n42: \n43: ### Task 3: Create cmd/workloadmanager directory structure\n44: - [ ] Create cmd/workloadmanager directory\n45: - [ ] Create cmd/workloadmanager/main.go\n46: - [ ] Create cmd/workloadmanager/flags.go\n47: - [ ] Create cmd/workloadmanager/main_test.go\n48: - [ ] Verify directory structure matches design\n49: \n50: **Verification**: Run `ls -la cmd/workloadmanager/` and verify all files are created\n51: \n52: ---\n53: \n54: ### Task 4: Implement cmd/workloadmanager/flags.go\n55: - [ ] Define port flag (default: \"8080\")\n56: - [ ] Define redis-addr flag (default: \"localhost:6379\")\n57: - [ ] Define redis-password flag (default: \"\")\n58: - [ ] Define redis-db flag (default: 0)\n59: - [ ] Define kubeconfig flag (default: \"\")\n60: - [ ] Define metrics-bind-address flag (default: \":8080\")\n61: - [ ] Define health-probe-bind-address flag (default: \":8081\")\n62: - [ ] Define leader-elect flag (default: false)\n63: - [ ] Add proper flag documentation\n64: - [ ] Export getter functions for each flag\n65: \n66: **Verification**: Run `./workloadmanager --help` and verify all flags are displayed\n67: \n68: ---\n69: \n70: ### Task 5: Implement cmd/workloadmanager/main.go - Package and imports\n71: - [ ] Declare main package\n72: - [ ] Import context package\n73: - [ ] Import flag package\n74: - [ ] Import os package\n75: - [ ] Import os/signal package\n76: - [ ] Import syscall package\n77: - [ ] Import time package\n78: - [ ] Import github.com/redis/go-redis/v9 package\n79: - [ ] Import k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes package\n80: - [ ] Import k8