with project testing framework\n\n### Configuration Changes\n\nNo configuration changes required in existing components.\n\n### Deployment Impact\n\n- New Python package module\n- Requires CodeInterpreter service to be deployed\n- No changes to existing services","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775876578902,"end":1775876578925}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876578927,"sessionID":"ses_2858327ebffeT1wJYh76T71bKz","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7d25080014SLCCow5z64cB3","messageID":"msg_d7a7cffe7001fpPSUl3KWQvYoB","sessionID":"ses_2858327ebffeT1wJYh76T71bKz","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-b89fec6b548f4824948a877a8faa0e66","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-027\n- **Title**: SDK CodeInterpreterClient\n- **Module**: sdk-python\n- **Language**: Python\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: In Progress\n\n## Description\n\nPython SDK client for interacting with the CodeInterpreter service, providing a high-level interface for code execution, session management, and result retrieval.\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- python-sdk (base SDK infrastructure)\n- httpx (HTTP client)\n- pydantic (data validation)\n- typing (type hints)\n\n## Related Changes\n\nNone\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n## Deferred Items\n\n[To be filled during implementation]","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/CHANGE.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/CHANGE.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775876578887,"end":1775876578926}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876578928,"sessionID":"ses_2858327ebffeT1wJYh76T71bKz","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7d9eeb001H7WQ3XlnKR4cUR","messageID":"msg_d7a7cffe7001fpPSUl3KWQvYoB","sessionID":"ses_2858327ebffeT1wJYh76T71bKz","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-9b2614a362844e5b930a0a6ac7c4f885","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient Specification\n\n## Module: sdk-python\n\n### CodeInterpreterClient Class\n\n#### Constructor\n\n```python\nclass CodeInterpreterClient:\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        base_url: str,\n        api_key: Optional[str] = None,\n        timeout: int = 30,\n        max_retries: int = 3\n    ) -> None\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `base_url`: Base URL of the CodeInterpreter service\n- `api_key`: Optional API key for authentication\n- `timeout`: Request timeout in seconds (default: 30)\n- `max_retries`: Maximum number of retry attempts (default: 3)\n\n#### Session Management Methods\n\n##### create_session\n\n```python\nasync def create_session(\n    self,\n    workspace_id: str,\n    timeout: int = 300,\n    metadata: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None\n) -> Session\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `workspace_id`: ID of the workspace\n- `timeout`: Session timeout in seconds (default: 300)\n- `metadata`: Optional metadata dictionary\n\n**Returns:** `Session` object\n\n**Raises:** `SessionCreationError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n##### get_session\n\n```python\nasync def get_session(self, session_id: str) -> Session\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `session_id`: ID of the session\n\n**Returns:** `Session` object\n\n**Raises:** `SessionNotFoundError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n##### list_sessions\n\n```python\nasync def list_sessions(\n    self,\n    workspace_id: Optional[str] = None,\n    limit: int = 100,\n    offset: int = 0\n) -> List[Session]\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `workspace_id`: Optional workspace ID to filter by\n- `limit`: Maximum number of sessions to return (default: 100)\n- `offset`: Pagination offset (default: 0)\n\n**Returns:** List of `Session` objects\n\n**Raises:** `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n##### delete_session\n\n```python\nasync def delete_session(self, session_id: str) -> None\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `session_id`: ID of the session\n\n**Raises:** `SessionNotFoundError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n#### Code Execution Methods\n\n##### execute_code\n\n```python\nasync def execute_code(\n    self,\n    session_id: str,\n    code: str,\n    timeout: Optional[int] = None\n) -> ExecutionResult\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `session_id`: ID of the session\n- `code`: Python code to execute\n- `timeout`: Optional execution timeout in seconds\n\n**Returns:** `ExecutionResult` object\n\n**Raises:** `SessionNotFoundError`, `ExecutionError`, `TimeoutError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n##### execute_code_async\n\n```python\nasync def execute_code_async(\n    self,\n    session_id: str,\n    code: str,\n    timeout: Optional[int] = None\n) -> ExecutionJob\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `session_id`: ID of the session\n- `code`: Python code to execute\n- `timeout`: Optional execution timeout in seconds\n\n**Returns:** `ExecutionJob` object\n\n**Raises:** `SessionNotFoundError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n##### get_execution_result\n\n```python\nasync def get_execution_result(self, job_id: str) -> ExecutionResult\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `job_id`: ID of the execution job\n\n**Returns:** `ExecutionResult` object\n\n**Raises:** `JobNotFoundError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n## Data Models\n\n### Session\n\n```python\nclass Session(BaseModel):\n    session_id: str\n    workspace_id: str\n    status: SessionStatus  # Enum: CREATING, ACTIVE, TERMINATED, ERROR\n    created_at: datetime\n    updated_at: datetime\n    timeout: int\n    metadata: Dict[str, str]\n```\n\n### SessionStatus\n\n```python\nclass SessionStatus(str, Enum):\n    CREATING = \"creating\"\n    ACTIVE = \"active\"\n    TERMINATED = \"terminated\"\n    ERROR = \"error\"\n```\n\n### ExecutionResult\n\n```python\nclass ExecutionResult(BaseModel):\n    job_id: str\n    session_id: str\n    status: ExecutionStatus  # Enum: PENDING, RUNNING, COMPLETED, FAILED\n    output: str\n    error: Optional[str]\n    execution_time: float\n    created_at: datetime\n    completed_at: Optional[datetime]\n```\n\n### ExecutionStatus\n\n```python\nclass ExecutionStatus(str, Enum):\n    PENDING = \"pending\"\n    RUNNING = \"running\"\n    COMPLETED = \"completed\"\n    FAILED = \"failed\"\n```\n\n### ExecutionJob\n\n```python\nclass ExecutionJob(BaseModel):\n    job_id: str\n    session_id: str\n    status: ExecutionStatus\n    created_at: datetime\n```\n\n## Exception Hierarchy\n\n```\nCodeInterpreterException\n├── AuthenticationError\n├── ConnectionError\n├── SessionError\n│   ├── SessionCreationError\n│   └── SessionNotFoundError\n├── ExecutionError\n│   ├── JobNotFoundError\n│   └── TimeoutError\n└── ValidationError\n```\n\n## HTTP Endpoints\n\n### Session Endpoints\n\n- `POST /v1/sessions` - Create session\n- `GET /v1/sessions/{session_id}` - Get session\n- `GET /v1/sessions` - List sessions\n- `DELETE /v1/sessions/{session_id}` - Delete session\n\n### Execution Endpoints\n\n- `POST /v1/sessions/{session_id}/execute` - Execute code\n- `GET /v1/jobs/{job_id}` - Get execution result","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-027/spec.md","time":{"start":1775876578899,"end":1775876578927}}}}
